            <scopecontent id="aspace_d47a2a934bf5dab24260057796d87eca">
               <head>Scope and Contents</head>
               <p>The series is arranged alphabetically. Correspondence with Woolverton's wife, Frances Curtis Woolverton includes a detailed inventory created by John F. Woolverton for the first two folders of letters.</p>
               <p>Other materials documenting the Woolverton family can be found at the Huntingdon County Historical Society (Huntingdon, PA) and the Bishop Payne Library (Alexandria, VA).</p>
